Partitioned Survival Model (PSM) Parameters

Source: R/data.R
l_psm_parameters.Rd

This list contains the Partitioned Survival Model (PSM) parameters including various cost, probability, and utility values used in the model.

Usage

l_psm_parameters

Format

A list with the following components:

body_weight

Body weight in kilograms, 15.

GD2_unit_mg

Unit dose of Dinutuximab β (GD2) in milligrams, 20.

GD2_dose_days

Number of days on Dinutuximab β per cycle, 5.

GD2_unit_price

Unit price of Dinutuximab β, 8790.26.

TT_unit_mg

Unit dose of Isotretinoin (TT) in milligrams, 10.

TT_dose_days

Number of days for Isotretinoin dosing, 14.

TT_unit_price

Unit price of Isotretinoin, 0.24.

GD2_aEvents_names

Names of adverse events for GD2:

fever

Fever

diarrhea

Diarrhea

vomiting

Vomiting

infection

Infection

hypersensitivity_reaction

Hypersensitivity reaction

capillary_leak

Capillary leak

prob_fever

Probability of fever, 0.18.

prob_diarrhea

Probability of diarrhea, 0.07.

prob_vomiting

Probability of vomiting, 0.06.

prob_infection

Probability of infection, 0.21.

prob_hypersensitivity_reaction

Probability of hypersensitivity reaction, 0.11.

prob_capillary_leak

Probability of capillary leak, 0.06.

cost_fever

Cost of fever, 1.98.

cost_diarrhea

Cost of diarrhea, 3.2.

cost_vomiting

Cost of vomiting, 8.45.

cost_infection

Cost of infection, 222.33.

cost_hypersensitivity_reaction

Cost of hypersensitivity reaction, 4.13.

cost_capillary_leak

Cost of capillary leak, 307.37.

cost_pain

Cost of pain, 6.36.

cost_laboratory

Cost of laboratory services, 141.45.

cost_hospitalisation

Cost of hospitalisation, 3763.62.

Temo_unit_mg

Unit dose of Temozolomide (Temo) in milligrams, 50.

Temo_dose_days

Number of days on Temozolomide per cycle, 5.

Temo_unit_price

Unit price of Temozolomide, 15.34.

Iri_unit_mg

Unit dose of Irinotecan (Iri) in milligrams, 40.

Iri_dose_days

Number of days on Irinotecan per cycle, 5.

Iri_unit_price

Unit price of Irinotecan, 4.4.

u_EFS

Utility value for Event-Free Survival (EFS), 0.84.

u_PPS

Utility value for Post-Progression Survival (PPS), 0.56.
